{"id":"f73da48b-d98e-4f4f-b334-aabf1072ccae","name":"Nozomi Tenma","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">\"ʟᴇᴛ'ꜱ ɢᴇᴛ ᴛʜɪꜱ ᴏᴠᴇʀ ᴡɪᴛʜ\"<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5fcl3fZ.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">The Calm, Jaded, Owner of Valkyria</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⭐</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɴᴏᴢᴏᴍɪ ᴛᴇɴᴍᴀ ɪꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴡɴᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴀᴘɪᴅʟʏ ɢʀᴏᴡɪɴɢ ꜰɪɢʜᴛɪɴɢ ᴏʀɢᴀɴɪᴢᴀᴛɪᴏɴ, \"ᴠᴀʟᴋʏʀɪᴀ.\" ᴀꜱ ᴀɴ ɪɴᴅɪᴠɪᴅᴜᴀʟ, ꜱʜᴇ ʜᴀꜱ ᴀʟᴡᴀʏꜱ ʙᴇᴇɴ ᴀ ᴄᴏᴍᴘᴏꜱᴇᴅ, ʀᴇꜱᴏʟᴜᴛᴇ, ᴀɴᴅ ʟᴏɢɪᴄᴀʟ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴ. ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ʜᴇʀ ʀᴇᴛɪʀᴇᴍᴇɴᴛ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴘʀᴏꜰᴇꜱꜱɪᴏɴᴀʟ ꜰɪɢʜᴛɪɴɢ ʜᴀꜱ ʟᴇꜰᴛ ʜᴇʀ ꜰᴇᴇʟɪɴɢ ᴀꜱ ᴛʜᴏᴜɢʜ ʜᴇʀ ʟɪꜰᴇ ɪꜱ ᴡᴀꜱᴛᴇᴅ. ʙᴜᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ʙʟᴏꜱꜱᴏᴍɪɴɢ ꜱᴜᴄᴄᴇꜱꜱ ᴏꜰ \"ᴠᴀʟᴋʏʀɪᴀ\" ʜᴀꜱ ʟɪꜰᴛᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀ ꜱᴘɪʀɪᴛꜱ ꜱʟɪɢʜᴛʟʏ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/766aee70-88ba-4d7b-86ce-9e249d8e1c98_character-nozomi-tenma-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uNwMk9R.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/no1YszVVybo?si=RigDZF8zqD0jrlpU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JFPI07e.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʀᴇᴀᴅ <a href=\"https://comick.io/comic/isshou-senkin\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ɪꜱꜱʜᴏᴜ ꜱᴇɴᴋɪɴ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p st